Required Karma Value of 100 or more.

Andrew, it's good to see you... hehe, you look
lively, which is great.

So, what's this talk about... You didn't call me
just to tell old stories, did you?

Well, there's no need to rush that much... But I
guess I can't help it. Let's get straight to the
point.

You know that this inn, Nengoro, is relatively
safe for staying overnight, right?

Because of that, sometimes magical girls also stay
here, emitting a strong scent of lust...

Well, it's fine as long as they stay as guests,
but occasionally there are some disrespectful
individuals who stay without paying.

I thought it was about time to apply some
moxibustion around here...

Hey, wait a minute. You're not seriously asking us
to fight against magical girls, right? That's not
a joke. They're not opponents we can handle.

Well... I prepared this. \C[3]Deceptive
Incense\C[0]. It's specifically made to work on
magical girls...

If you burn this in the room, even magical girls
will become defenseless, and then... Andrew, it's
time for your huge cock to shine.

Hehe, so you're saying I can fuck her as much as I
want?

Exactly. This is one way to show my gratitude for
the debt you owed me in the past...

Well, in that case, it's simple. We just have to
target the all-you-can-eat magical girls who stay
for free.
